title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 52-6.10 - Required records of tissue acquisition, testing, processing and storage
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 §§ 52-6.10 - Required records of tissue acquisition, testing, processing and storage

State Regulations

Each skin bank shall maintain donation records as required by Subpart 52-2 of this Part. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10
§§
52-6.10

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
